event_entries.author: Admin
event_entries.title: Community Development Event by IWA India Foundation in Mulappamon
event_entries.short_description: Join the IWA India Foundation’s impactful event at Mulappamon, showcasing initiatives in education, healthcare, and community support. This gathering aims to further the foundation's mission of uplifting underprivileged communities.
event_entries.long_description: The IWA India Foundation is hosting an event at Mulappamon, focusing on humanitarian efforts in education, healthcare, and community welfare. Founded by Dr. PA Muhammed Farooq Naeemi, the foundation has been actively supporting marginalized communities since 2013. This event will highlight ongoing projects and explore future initiatives. Attendees will gain insight into the foundation’s mission and discover ways to get involved in meaningful community support efforts. For inquiries, contact +91 8523 000 111, +91 8086 660 088, or email iwaindiafoundation@gmail.com.
